			</ul>
			<p>這些附加選擇可通過鼠標右擊<img  style="position: relative; top: 3px; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-color: #808080;" src="chrome://furiganainjector/skin/status_icon/default.png"alt="振" />的圖標即可實現。</p>
